    <outline text="Sally was ACTUALLY the first African-American FLOTUS, not Michelle Obama. She just didn’t have the legitimacy that Michelle had">
      <outline text="It *LOOKS* like that Sallie lived in Monticello during Jefferson’s terms of office. TJ would stay at Monticello for MONTHS at a time, so it wasn’t as if he didn’t have ready access to her"/>
