    <outline text="TJ and Washington were both terrible with money and both had EXTRAVAGANT lifestyles and yet were not that good at income generation or investments or money management"/>
    <outline text="So it looks like the core idea is that there is a love triangle (or love square):">
      <outline text="Martha Wayles Skelton Jefferson got officially named as FLOTUS (even though she’s dead) — which shows you just how much the Founders lived in the Past"/>
